Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.34,0:01:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.37,0:01:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.94,0:01:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.82,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.55,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘伊榭莲娜的悲恋’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月球的另一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.33,0:02:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浮游着多个太空都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用独裁手段支配地球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨比家支配的宇宙都市国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这些漂流宇宙的圆筒建筑物内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有着人类生存的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个都市的直径有6公里阔及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.72,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长30公里以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里面有着和自然一样的环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使人可以像在地球般地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.01,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION国的宇宙攻击军司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔中将正从前线赶回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和半年前一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本没有加强工事建设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙殖民地是利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离心力来制造重心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们在里面的大地生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是ZION公国的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹姆市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可让卡尔玛白白牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这会影响我们萨比家的声誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在已经觉得很伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.16,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报告陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔中将及基西莉亚少将已从前线赶回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他们入来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们俩都回来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，别太伤心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛作梦也想不到联邦军的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会打败他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到现在我还未可接受他的死讯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只在忆念卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不可战胜的，德兹尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛很聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连我也很佩服他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且将来也会胜过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是五星上将的好人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该以沉重心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.28,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来追掉卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你久等了，依榭莲娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前日的晚会上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已见过你动人丰姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有将校都异口同声地赞你美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里就是上校的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在一定是很伤心的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们一定会为上校报仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜小姐，我们一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗达中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.41,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我乘上卡乌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜小姐，你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很憎恨害死卡尔玛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是只能开一枪也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一定要报这个仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗达中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么说也还未是时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了这里已经和到达了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军会来接我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很心急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想第一个落地面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一股很强大的气流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是风眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在本舰进入乱气流内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将有持续的震荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为里面有保险制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不能投出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你是机械天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.86,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以两个一起用吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是同一样的东西呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,12号地点发现敌军！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有3台卡乌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,探测器显示是卡乌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一共3台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修理好GUNDAM了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随时可以出动了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎好像故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，需要紧急降落吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差一点便到我军范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许有援军来呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先想办法到联邦军制空圈内较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出去反会被气流卷走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我认为会有利才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，我们一次过尽量跳过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试一试吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标机动战士出来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他杀死了卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何，我也会助你复仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开炮，开炮，射他下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，小心别接近炮门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找死的便来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2号机去支援3号机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们太可恶了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还有战机吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很对不起，在多次作战后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以用的都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是夏亚少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来助你一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚，我是卡尔玛上校直属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫罗达中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁也好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起瞄准控制室攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM心脏部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先去攻击木马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要集中破坏便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使卡尔玛战死的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示对萨比家的忠诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何一方面也不会有损失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军有电报来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对White Base的支持仍在争议中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来不会有援军来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连玛吉路达中尉作为中间人而来一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也引起非议...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道他们根本想我们去送死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还未读完全封电报呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们准备收留难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请向S109
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和N23地点方面航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，转向1.5方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.31,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌军从前方来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了，保险擎坏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！左后方被击中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向舵也受损了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没法控制方向！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急降落，大家扶隐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有安全带的请扣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,着陆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好方法可以夺取母舰到手吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，你做得相当好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非我的驾驶术了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是White Base性能出色罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太谦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你没受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以帮我看看难民的情况吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂时还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落到地面再算吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不可让凶手走脱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定...一定要杀死他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我将引擎部份做好应急处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该可以支持下去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎部份可以用了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有百分之25左右动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.91,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉强可以应付！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边也可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想不到母舰如此捱得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！我们要快离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若再受袭的话便不能再动了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不和阿姆罗和良联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未联络到他们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍未收到他们的报告呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长 队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在已有数名难民逃到外面去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能再忍受下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！别去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面很危险的 别去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你回来，很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人可能就在附近的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION军想要的只是母舰和GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我们根本就没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在母舰才危险呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快给我们走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们走不掉的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 他是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.03,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛的追悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我们一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，现在是战争之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为让国民统一，情绪高涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该用国葬方法来追悼才适合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次卡尔玛的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非单就他一人的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是ZION全国的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也赞成大哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要先处分夏亚才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能尽责保护卡尔玛的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处罚他可给人民一个警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些事应该在你权力范围内做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.21,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在最重要的是举行仪式，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛一直在人民心目中很有人缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以透过用国葬的仪式来追悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.06,0:17:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以激起人民对联邦的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于夏亚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德兹尔你将他降职处分吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父王，你是ZION的国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请快指示应该怎样处理...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，掩护我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！大家集中火力攻击机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再继续加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把机动战士毁灭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盾抵挡不住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.27,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.52,0:18:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗达中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手不行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.57,0:19:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我来驾驶吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依榭莲娜小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛的仇便报不了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.49,0:19:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要为卡尔玛报仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟！不知那里坏了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！你没受伤吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.56,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，看来GUNDAM故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出去看看情况！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡乌上可能有士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.10,0:20:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗达中尉...中尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你就是杀卡尔玛的凶手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凶手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是...凶手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别人是靠不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜力，有人问起我的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.33,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便说计算机系统绕坏了就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是救援队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说我是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.78,0:23:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗疲倦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.67,0:23:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是新的敌人兰巴·拉尔降临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.75,0:23:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机动战士强大的破坏力玩弄着GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而此时听到ZION万岁的呼喊声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.58,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.21,0:23:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘ZION的威胁’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

